{"tid":1670943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港警去台押犯就得】揭港府雙重標準！3年前赴台押藏屍犯回港 今拒台來港押犯","createTime":"2019-10-23T07:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:15:38.000Z","uid":70786,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e927a31ef0a051e511f3eb1b864acc08536d6ce0","tid":1670943,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191023/60185884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60185884&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=05be110c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60185884&h=e99ea095\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191023/60185884</a><br />\n<br />\n特區政府拒絕台灣要求，不准台灣派執法人員來港，把在台灣殺害香港女友的陳同佳帶返台灣受審，聲稱這是「跨境執法，完全不能接受」；指陳出獄後，可在自己選擇的人陪同下赴台，台方在陳抵埗後，可將他拘捕。但事實上，本港正審理的荃灣工廈石棺藏屍案中，便首次由港警到台灣「跨境執法」，將3名疑犯曾祥欣、劉錫豪和張善恒押解返港。大批網民回顧3年前的報道，嘲林鄭月娥政府「#選擇性合作 #唔係話一個中國咩 #政治操作」、「以前有，現在竟然拒絕？林鄭還不是政治計算？」<br />\n<br />\n案中4名男疑犯3年前犯案後，逃往台灣台北，其中18歲疑犯「小草」擔心被人滅口，主動向台警舉報。台警追查下，在台北板橋區一間出租屋帶走3名疑犯，關押於新北市移民署羈留室。小草先被遞解出境返港後，之後3名男疑犯由台警送往桃園機場，由抵台的香港警方押解返港。當時香港警方與台灣刑事局人員，在空橋內完成交接程序，直接搭乘國泰航空班機返港，是港台首次在桃園機場空橋移交疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n究竟係邊個唔尊重台灣一清二楚<br />\n又俾子彈小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92521f3fb86da99f83fb73e3d0afd8156b1ff889","tid":1670943,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f2de77f2437c14bf771860170c1014a65406083","tid":1670943,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0847c9a4c49c987f655014319fd7959074a45854","tid":1670943,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"我係陳同佳都會決定自首, 因為明知台灣唔夠料耡佢死刑, 仲有機走甩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670202</a>"},{"pid":"7ee2f703714e3d368684806c9c520ac2f8551cc0","tid":1670943,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"推到小英拎嚟屌港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5cf5d51383c260aa4f2b70781111af37a5cf36","tid":1670943,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"政府發言人唔係好快手衝出嚟柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23788549d40780ebdc6871f66352e4535be884fd","tid":1670943,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"台灣一直主張嘅司法互助<br />\n港府有求於人就可以<br />\n台灣想嚟香港押犯就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a747990727600ce02fbd136122e43752adbb9","tid":1670943,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"俾殺人犯用旅客身份上機<br />\n唔俾台灣來港押犯以保障同機人安全<br />\n777唔安排專機俾大粒癦？<br />\n<br />\n支那走狗777快d拆彈啦<br />\n考第一好叻架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5a61332f2e12194a0fc37dd7d4139540909935","tid":1670943,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭真係柒出國際！"},{"pid":"5a01c5f22fc8f27967126ffd4a3137cc1ce59ed4","tid":1670943,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f2d6da414f16d32bb74282cec2f712e89790a08","tid":1670943,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"將大粒癦單嘢發大嚟搞，拖機管局、民航處、航空公司落水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"186bfd4c2158b5e4520d89fed40e70a4e27e3b